OL,3,CLabour MP calls on Reform UK to stop
OL,4,Cboycott of local newspaper
OL,6,FA Nottinghamshire Labour MP has
OL,7,Fwritten to Reform leader Nigel Farage
OL,8,Fdemanding he reverses the decision of
OL,9,Fhis party to boycott a local newspaper.
OL,11,FThe leader of Nottinghamshire County
OL,12,FCouncil Mick Barton announced on
OL,13,FThursday he would ban his 41
OL,14,Fcouncillors from speaking to
OL,15,FNottingham Post and its website
OL,16,FNottinghamshire Live.
