OL,3,CLabour MP calls on Reform UK to stop
OL,4,Cboycott of local newspaper
OL,6,FIn a letter, the MP for Gedling said:
OL,7,F"Journalists provide one of the means
OL,8,Fthrough which local people can ask
OL,9,Fquestions and get answers from their
OL,10,Fpoliticians.
OL,12,F"So, when councillors refuse to speak
OL,13,Fto local newspapers, they are refusing
OL,14,Fto be accountable to the very people
OL,15,Fthey are meant to represent.
