OL,3,CLabour MP calls on Reform UK to stop
OL,4,Cboycott of local newspaper
OL,6,F"That is why I am calling on you to
OL,7,Freverse this decision immediately.
OL,8,FRestore proper engagement with
OL,9,FNottinghamshire Live, and make clear
OL,10,Fto your Party's councillors that they
OL,11,Fare accountable to the people they
OL,12,Fserve."
OL,14,FPayne said he would like to see Reform
OL,15,FUK have "proper engagement with
OL,16,FNottinghamshire Live.''
OL,18,FNottinghamshire Live has local
OL,19,Fdemocracy reporters who regularly
OL,20,Fattend council meetings and report on
OL,21,Fcouncil decisions.
