OL,3,CLabour MP calls on Reform UK to stop
OL,4,Cboycott of local newspaper
OL,6,FThe newspaper and website will also no
OL,7,Flonger be invited to council events.
OL,9,FThe Nottingham Post was founded in
OL,10,F1878 and has been operating in
OL,11,FNottingham for almost 150 years.
OL,13,FThe decision has been described as
OL,14,F"chilling" by the newspaper's Agenda
OL,15,FEditor and as a "massive attack on
OL,16,Flocal democracy" by its editor, who
OL,17,Fwarned it was a "worrying sign of
OL,18,Fthings to come" if Reform gain any
OL,19,Fmore power.
