OL,3,CLabour MP calls on Reform UK to stop
OL,4,Cboycott of local newspaper
OL,6,F"For this reason, we will not be
OL,7,Fengaging with Nottinghamshire Live or
OL,8,Fwith any other media outlet we
OL,9,Fconsider to be consistently
OL,10,Fmisrepresenting our policies, actions,
OL,11,For intentions. Selective reporting,
OL,12,Fdistortion, or omission undermines not
OL,13,Fonly our Council but also the right of
OL,14,Fthe public to accurate information."
